{"tid":2150902,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"［估唔到］股票市場係一新戰線","createTime":"2020-08-11T06:33:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T06:44:19.000Z","uid":218211,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fcd5191c0339b7d723d70c42ea5ac59d536bb0a2","tid":2150902,"uid":218211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T06:33:44.000Z","msg":"香港人冇票投就走去投資<br />\n一隻282一夜之間升左至少18倍<br />\n令國際觸目<br />\n亦令港府束手無策<br />\n<br />\n係佢地拉肥佬黎而引起<br />\n係國安法既實施之下<br />\n香港變得更「繁榮」同「穩定」<br />\n<br />\n漲停就係操控市場或者政治打壓<br />\n有違香港咁多年以黎作為國際金融中心<br />\n擁護既市場自由<br />\n<br />\n自2019年，香港人已經脫胎換骨<br />\n估唔到今日又開闢左一條新戰線<br />\n只有繼續上<br />\n先自可以令國際金融既戰線上引黎更大既迴響<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利：<a href=\"http://未持有282.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E6%9C%AA%E6%8C%81%E6%9C%89282.HK&d=ukYMMJnQLP7OtwhP8v88lB3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=419b4419\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">未持有282.HK</a> 壹傳媒<br />\n<br />\n光<br />\n時"},{"pid":"e5297f3d56148ce3853409bdc376e5b99ee4e6f3","tid":2150902,"uid":218211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T06:35:36.000Z","msg":"蘋果唔可以死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbda106f7d063f50bb7ec04b16e788d74cb0d12c","tid":2150902,"uid":218211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T06:36:28.000Z","msg":"We shall fight on: Next Digital !"},{"pid":"c93eff1f4151a2c4e4180229d3ea89d6f153d988","tid":2150902,"uid":218211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T06:36:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61686921322152c4421f53ff733d1e26f11836bc","tid":2150902,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T06:37:52.000Z","msg":"買多左蘋果既手足 唔好齋擺屋企 當派報紙咁直頭擺去隔離鄰舍門口！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2150861\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2150861</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d9bc4a3af1011228749f23ae35adcddbe2ae48f6","tid":2150902,"uid":170244,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T06:43:09.000Z","msg":"等睇熱狗出黎認屎認屁,<br />\n話&quot;皇上一早就講過&quot;股市抗爭&quot;呢樣野啦&quot;<br />\n<br />\n利申:持有&quot;金錢師&quot;頭兩卷,<br />\n但好撚憎熱狗"},{"pid":"be84a01007209aeb8be6535941b36f1f09d2b89d","tid":2150902,"uid":55672,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T06:44:19.000Z","msg":"疫情下的黃色經濟圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}